P.	Find departments where more than one female is working.

mysql> select department,count(department) from employee where gender= 'female'group by department having count(department)>1;
+------------+-------------------+
| department | count(department) |
+------------+-------------------+
| HR         |                 2 |
| IT         |                 2 |
| Marketing  |                 2 |
+------------+-------------------+
