U.	List top 3 departments with highest total salary.
mysql> select department,sum(salary) from employee group by department having sum(salary) order by sum(salary)desc limit 3;
+------------+-------------+
| department | sum(salary) |
+------------+-------------+
| IT         |   356000.00 |
| Finance    |   241000.00 |
| Marketing  |   155000.00 |
+------------+-------------+
3 rows in set (0.00 sec)
